item.title: No More Sticker Shock With Managed Services
item.dc:creator: ins_emerson
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row gap="35"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Watch how Taylor Lewis revolutionised their IT infrastructure with the help of Innvoke." use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_separator color="custom" align="align_left" border_width="3" el_width="20" accent_color="#36ab9c"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Project Overview:" font_container="tag:h5|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1556003180993{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="While the benefits of moving certain business applications to the cloud are widely understood, many organisations can be reticent to make the change – often for fear of disrupting their day-to-day processes, making an existing technology investment redundant, or risking the security of their data. With Taylor Lewis, however, the opposite was the case." font_container="tag:p|font_size:16px|text_align:left|line_height:29px" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="font-weight-500"][vc_empty_space height="30px"][vc_custom_heading text="Challenge:" font_container="tag:h5|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1556003549922{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="Like many businesses today, the management team at a Taylor Lewis struggled with their IT systems. During the company’s start -up phase, they inherited several old computers as part of a sublease agreement on their new office space. What seemed like a bargain for this brand new company turned out to be a major headache. With old equipment patched together by nothing more than a part-time computer handyman, they were having connectivity issues and problems with data access, file sharing and backup, along with virus and security concerns." font_container="tag:p|font_size:16px|text_align:left|line_height:29px" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="font-weight-500"][vc_empty_space height="30px"][vc_custom_heading text="Solution:" font_container="tag:h5|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1556003559659{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="Internal and remote users can now easily collaborate and share documents, printers and other important system resources. Appropriate e-mail retention and virtually unlimited storage could now be implemented to facilitate proper reporting and data retention compliance. Also, as a result of centralized file sharing, the number of e-mail attachments was greatly reduced and substantially reduced the individual mailbox folder size." font_container="tag:p|font_size:16px|text_align:left|line_height:29px" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="font-weight-500"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1556018751510{margin-top: 80px !important;margin-bottom: 100px !important;}"][vc_column][vc_single_image image="1524" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1556017718874{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="What we did" font_container="tag:h6|text_align:left|color:%23747e80" use_theme_fonts="yes" el_class="letter-spacing-2 text-uppercase" css=".vc_custom_1556011661690{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="With the solutions provided by Innvoke, this company was able to see immediate results in their productivity.
